sparqlQuery:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri
WHERE {
        res:Bruce_Lee dbo:child ?child . 
        ?child dbo:child ?uri .
}

languageToQuestion.en: Give me the grandchildren of Bruce Lee.
languageToQuestion.de: Gib mir die Enkel von Bruce Lee.
languageToQuestion.es: Dame todos los nietos de Bruce Lee.
languageToQuestion.it: Dammi i nipoti di Bruce Lee.
languageToQuestion.fr: Donne-moi tous les petit-enfants de Bruce Lee.
languageToQuestion.nl: Toon alle kleinkinderen van Bruce Lee.

sparqlQuery:
PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> 
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> 
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> 
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> 
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri 
WHERE { 
        ?uri rdf:type yago:StatesOfTheUnitedStates . 
        ?uri dbp:governor res:Sean_Parnell . 
}

languageToQuestion.en: Sean Parnell is the governor of which U.S. state?
languageToQuestion.de: Von welchem US-Bundesstaat ist Sean Parnell der Gouverneur?
languageToQuestion.es: ¿De qué estado americano es Sean Parnell el gobernador?
languageToQuestion.it: Di quale stato americano Sean Parnell è governatore?
languageToQuestion.fr: Quel est l'état américain dont Sean Parnelle st le gouverneur?
languageToQuestion.nl: Sean Parnell is de gouverneur van welke staat van de Verenigde Staten?
languageToQuestion.ro: Sean Parnell este guvernatorul cărui stat american?

sparqlQuery:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> 
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> 
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> 
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> 
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri 
WHERE { 
        ?uri rdf:type dbo:Weapon .  
        ?uri dbp:designer ?x . 
        res:Uzi dbp:designer ?x . 
        FILTER (?uri != res:Uzi) 
}

languageToQuestion.en: Which other weapons did the designer of the Uzi develop?
languageToQuestion.de: Welche anderen Waffen hat der Erfinder der Uzi entwickelt?
languageToQuestion.es: ¿Qué otras armas desarrolló el inventor del Uzi?
languageToQuestion.it: Quali altre armi sono state progettate dall'inventore dell'Uzi?
languageToQuestion.fr: Quels autres armes ont été developées par l'inventeur de l'Uzi?
languageToQuestion.nl: Welke andere wapens heeft de uitvinder van de Uzi ontwikkeld?
languageToQuestion.ro: Ce alte arme a realizat proiectantul Uzi?
